en.name: 6B45 body armor
en.description: The 6B45 body armor, designed to protect personnel from shrapnel and small arms fire. Part of the Ratnik equipment system and has been in production since the 2010s as a replacement for the 6B43 model.

en.name: Interceptor OTV body armor (Woodland)
en.description: The Interceptor vest consists of a fabric Outer Tactical Vest (OTV) with dorsal and thoracic pockets and two protective ceramic-composite SAPI or ESAPI inserts. The Outer Tactical Vest (OTV) is a basic vest equipped with aramid fabric pouches that protect against ammunition fragments and 9mm handgun bullets. Woodland camouflage version.

en.name: NFM THOR Concealable Reinforced Vest body armor (Head Eyes)
en.description: A low-profile body armor manufactured by NFM. A version for those who really feel the Tarkov atmosphere.

weaponPresets._name: Бронежилет NFM THOR Concealable Reinforced Vest (Head, Eyes) Standart

en.name: NPP KlASS Korund-VM body armor (Kamysh)
en.description: The NPP KlASS Korund-VM heavy bulletproof vest, adopted by the units of the Ministry of Internal Affairs of Russia. Kamysh camouflage version.
